Package: thesisdownfsu
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown package
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kari", "Roberts", email = "kari.roberts.718@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: This is a modification of the thesisdown package by Chester Ismay for 
    Dissertation writers at Florida State University. Using the bookdown package LaTeX 
    and Word thesis templates from Florida State University, this package aims to 
    encourage reproducible research using simple Markdown syntax while embedding 
    all of the R code to produce plots and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Kari Roberts <kari.roberts.718@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    here,
    R.utils
Suggests:
    remotes,
    usethis
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - https://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
